*Jedem* kolače. (We are eating cake.)
Oni *jedu* ribu. (They are eating fish.)
Mi smo *jeli* hranu. (We have eaten food.)
Ona *jede* salatu. (She is eating salad.)
Oni *jednu* čašu vode. (They are drinking one glass of water.)
Mi smo *jedli* piletinu. (We have been eating chicken.)
Ona *jede* jabuke. (She is eating apples.)
Mi smo *jedli* sladoled. (We have been eating ice cream.)
Oni će *jesti* pizzu. (They will be eating pizza.)
Mi smo *jeli* svinjetinu. (We have been eating pork.)